Interface PrimitiveToVar<T,VT extends PrimitiveToVar<T,VT>>

Type Parameters:
T - the wrapper type
All Superinterfaces:

All Known Subinterfaces:
BooleanVar, ByteVar, CharVar, DoubleVar, FloatVar, IntVar, LongVar, ShortVar
public interface PrimitiveToVar<T,VT extends PrimitiveToVar<T,VT>> extends PrimitiveToVal<T>
This interface is used to convert Var of primitive type to Var of wrapper type, such as IntVar to Var<Integer>.
